data.description: LOCATION AND OPPORTUNITY! Welcome home to the beautiful Tannehill Preserve! This gorgeous 4 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath home has plenty of space for everyone.  You'll enjoy preparing meals in the large open kitchen with an island breakfast bar and dining space, highlighted with a tiled backsplash and plenty of cabinetry space. Beautiful hardwood floors in the main living area, a bedroom, and full bath downstairs, with two bedrooms, a master suite, and an entertaining common area with huge potential upstairs! Master bath detailed with a large tub, double sinks, and walk-in closets. Enjoy all the amenities of Tannehill Preserve; a community pool, walking trails, and a playground. Perfectly settled between Tuscaloosa and Birmingham, convenient to shopping, restaurants, and the new UAB Hospital opening in 2024! Don't miss this opportunity!
